select cast_info.note, title.title, char_name.id, complete_cast.subject_id, sum(complete_cast.movie_id) from char_name JOIN cast_info ON cast_info.person_role_id = char_name.id JOIN title ON title.id = cast_info.movie_id JOIN complete_cast ON complete_cast.movie_id = title.id where cast_info.note = '(film researcher)' AND complete_cast.subject_id > 2 group by cast_info.note, title.title, complete_cast.subject_id, char_name.id having sum(complete_cast.movie_id) = 2427152

select company_type.id, movie_companies.id, max(movie_companies.company_id) from movie_companies, company_type where company_type.id > 4 AND movie_companies.movie_id > 2387843 AND movie_companies.note >= '(????) (USA) (VHS)' group by company_type.id, movie_companies.id having max(movie_companies.company_id) >= 708

select title.md5sum, comp_cast_type.id, complete_cast.movie_id, movie_keyword.id, min(complete_cast.status_id) from comp_cast_type JOIN complete_cast ON complete_cast.status_id = comp_cast_type.id JOIN title ON title.id = complete_cast.movie_id JOIN movie_keyword ON movie_keyword.movie_id = title.id where comp_cast_type.id < 1 AND title.episode_nr < 54 group by title.md5sum, comp_cast_type.id, complete_cast.movie_id, movie_keyword.id having min(complete_cast.status_id) > 4 order by title.md5sum DESC

select title.imdb_index, movie_link.link_type_id from movie_link, title where title.series_years > '1996-????' AND title.phonetic_code < 'U5263' AND title.md5sum = 'e043157ee7b99e4bcc2fdf290a332164' AND movie_link.id > 15293 AND movie_link.linked_movie_id > 1394139 AND title.md5sum = '2ee4d131cde1335cedbb41fcb5065a6a' AND title.title > 'Flower''s Squirt Shower 4'

select movie_keyword.movie_id, title.series_years, cast_info.note from cast_info JOIN title ON title.id = cast_info.movie_id JOIN movie_keyword ON movie_keyword.movie_id = title.id where cast_info.person_role_id = 2359209 AND cast_info.id <= 26134417 AND cast_info.role_id = 9 order by cast_info.note DESC

select title.episode_nr, movie_keyword.id, title.series_years, count(movie_keyword.movie_id), max(title.series_years), sum(movie_keyword.id) from keyword JOIN movie_keyword ON movie_keyword.keyword_id = keyword.id JOIN title ON title.id = movie_keyword.movie_id where title.md5sum < '4cde064e298247ed97cfbe03bb39e3fc' AND keyword.phonetic_code > 'P4352' AND title.kind_id = 2 group by title.episode_nr, movie_keyword.id, title.series_years order by title.episode_nr ASC

select movie_info.movie_id, title.md5sum, link_type.id, movie_link.id from movie_info JOIN title ON title.id = movie_info.movie_id JOIN movie_link ON movie_link.movie_id = title.id JOIN link_type ON link_type.id = movie_link.link_type_id where title.imdb_index = 'II' AND title.id >= 563730 AND title.production_year < 1986 order by movie_info.movie_id ASC

select title.id, complete_cast.subject_id, keyword.phonetic_code, movie_keyword.id, comp_cast_type.kind from keyword JOIN movie_keyword ON movie_keyword.keyword_id = keyword.id JOIN title ON title.id = movie_keyword.movie_id JOIN complete_cast ON complete_cast.movie_id = title.id JOIN comp_cast_type ON comp_cast_type.id = complete_cast.status_id where keyword.id >= 104859 AND keyword.keyword <= 'civic-pride' AND complete_cast.movie_id >= 1923775 order by movie_keyword.id DESC, keyword.phonetic_code DESC

select keyword.keyword, movie_keyword.id from movie_keyword JOIN keyword ON keyword.id = movie_keyword.keyword_id where keyword.phonetic_code < 'P4352' AND movie_keyword.keyword_id <= 2926 AND movie_keyword.id >= 978617 AND movie_keyword.movie_id = 1882109 order by keyword.keyword DESC, movie_keyword.id DESC

select kind_type.id, title.series_years, aka_title.imdb_index, name.name_pcode_nf, cast_info.role_id from kind_type JOIN aka_title ON aka_title.kind_id = kind_type.id JOIN title ON title.id = aka_title.movie_id JOIN cast_info ON cast_info.movie_id = title.id JOIN name ON name.id = cast_info.person_id where aka_title.episode_of_id < 14559 AND aka_title.season_nr = 38 order by cast_info.role_id DESC, kind_type.id DESC

select cast_info.person_role_id, name.imdb_index, role_type.id, name.md5sum from aka_name JOIN name ON name.id = aka_name.person_id JOIN cast_info ON cast_info.person_id = name.id JOIN role_type ON role_type.id = cast_info.role_id where cast_info.id = 16259159 AND name.id > 1303966 AND cast_info.note <= '(as Reiner Schone)' AND role_type.id >= 9

select movie_keyword.movie_id, movie_link.movie_id, title.md5sum, link_type.link from movie_keyword JOIN title ON title.id = movie_keyword.movie_id JOIN movie_link ON movie_link.movie_id = title.id JOIN link_type ON link_type.id = movie_link.link_type_id where movie_link.linked_movie_id >= 1808225 AND link_type.link >= 'spin off from' AND title.series_years >= '2009-????' order by movie_link.movie_id ASC, movie_keyword.movie_id DESC, link_type.link DESC, title.md5sum ASC

select complete_cast.movie_id, title.episode_nr, movie_keyword.keyword_id, comp_cast_type.id from movie_keyword JOIN title ON title.id = movie_keyword.movie_id JOIN complete_cast ON complete_cast.movie_id = title.id JOIN comp_cast_type ON comp_cast_type.id = complete_cast.status_id where comp_cast_type.id >= 2 AND comp_cast_type.kind > 'complete+verified' AND title.episode_nr <= 29

select cast_info.note, cast_info.movie_id from role_type, cast_info where cast_info.movie_id > 1981690 AND cast_info.role_id = 6 AND cast_info.person_role_id < 1941616 AND cast_info.note <= '(as James Lichtscheidl)'

select complete_cast.movie_id, title.imdb_index, complete_cast.status_id from movie_info_idx JOIN title ON title.id = movie_info_idx.movie_id JOIN complete_cast ON complete_cast.movie_id = title.id where complete_cast.id = 48186 AND title.production_year < 1903 AND movie_info_idx.movie_id <= 919135 AND title.episode_of_id >= 966231

select comp_cast_type.kind, complete_cast.status_id, title.production_year, movie_info.info, sum(comp_cast_type.id) from comp_cast_type JOIN complete_cast ON complete_cast.status_id = comp_cast_type.id JOIN title ON title.id = complete_cast.movie_id JOIN movie_info ON movie_info.movie_id = title.id where movie_info.info_type_id < 65 AND movie_info.movie_id <= 2342737 AND title.md5sum < '6feeed89f6a89b5e9c266b5394c332be' group by movie_info.info, complete_cast.status_id, comp_cast_type.kind, title.production_year

select char_name.id, cast_info.person_role_id, role_type.id from role_type JOIN cast_info ON cast_info.role_id = role_type.id JOIN char_name ON char_name.id = cast_info.person_role_id where char_name.md5sum < 'c71bcc30ec4027737dbc83a044050e94' AND role_type.id >= 7 AND cast_info.person_id = 3095403 order by char_name.id DESC, role_type.id ASC

select keyword.keyword, keyword.phonetic_code from keyword, movie_keyword where movie_keyword.keyword_id >= 33929 AND keyword.id > 86959 AND keyword.phonetic_code >= 'N6253' AND movie_keyword.id > 735536 AND keyword.phonetic_code < 'P4352' order by keyword.phonetic_code DESC, keyword.keyword DESC

select keyword.phonetic_code, movie_keyword.movie_id, sum(movie_keyword.movie_id), max(movie_keyword.keyword_id) from keyword JOIN movie_keyword ON movie_keyword.keyword_id = keyword.id where movie_keyword.id = 4511292 AND keyword.id = 43184 AND keyword.phonetic_code <= 'N6253' group by keyword.phonetic_code, movie_keyword.movie_id order by keyword.phonetic_code DESC, movie_keyword.movie_id ASC

select movie_link.movie_id, title.season_nr, title.episode_of_id, avg(title.episode_nr), max(title.phonetic_code) from link_type, movie_link, title where title.imdb_index <= 'I' AND title.production_year > 1977 AND title.kind_id = 7 group by title.episode_of_id, title.season_nr, movie_link.movie_id order by movie_link.movie_id DESC

select aka_title.phonetic_code, title.phonetic_code, movie_info.note, max(aka_title.phonetic_code) from movie_info JOIN title ON title.id = movie_info.movie_id JOIN aka_title ON aka_title.movie_id = title.id where aka_title.kind_id < 7 AND title.md5sum < '438afc197bf5adfc49019f0496a3797e' AND aka_title.id = 89570 group by aka_title.phonetic_code, title.phonetic_code, movie_info.note

select title.season_nr, movie_companies.note, movie_link.id, link_type.id, max(title.episode_of_id) from link_type JOIN movie_link ON movie_link.link_type_id = link_type.id JOIN title ON title.id = movie_link.movie_id JOIN movie_companies ON movie_companies.movie_id = title.id where movie_companies.note > '(1979) (USA: Midwest) (theatrical) (dubbed)' AND movie_link.link_type_id = 4 group by movie_link.id, link_type.id, title.season_nr, movie_companies.note order by movie_companies.note DESC, title.season_nr DESC, movie_link.id ASC

select info_type.id, movie_companies.movie_id, company_name.name, movie_info_idx.movie_id, movie_companies.company_type_id from info_type JOIN movie_info_idx ON movie_info_idx.info_type_id = info_type.id JOIN title ON title.id = movie_info_idx.movie_id JOIN movie_companies ON movie_companies.movie_id = title.id JOIN company_name ON company_name.id = movie_companies.company_id where title.episode_of_id >= 806041 AND title.id >= 565537 order by company_name.name ASC

select person_info.info, max(person_info.note), min(person_info.person_id) from person_info where person_info.info > 'Music Album "Admitted" in March of 2011.' AND person_info.person_id < 1290899 AND person_info.info_type_id >= 24 group by person_info.info having min(person_info.person_id) = 1823584 AND max(person_info.note) < 'Anonymous' order by min(person_info.person_id) ASC, max(person_info.note) DESC

select movie_link.linked_movie_id, title.phonetic_code, title.title from movie_link JOIN title ON title.id = movie_link.movie_id JOIN movie_info ON movie_info.movie_id = title.id where title.md5sum <= 'ba830df41cf756fd345e2b9683690c19' AND movie_info.info_type_id >= 105 AND title.episode_nr >= 54 AND title.kind_id < 1 AND movie_info.id = 5941914

select role_type.id, char_name.name, cast_info.note from role_type JOIN cast_info ON cast_info.role_id = role_type.id JOIN char_name ON char_name.id = cast_info.person_role_id where role_type.role = 'actress' AND role_type.id <= 10 AND cast_info.person_id = 3603927 order by char_name.name DESC, cast_info.note DESC
